title: [Robes of Resistance]
description: Bolts of various fabrics line makeshift shelves along the wagon's walls.  Coat stands displaying outerwear garments in different sizes and colors stand sentry beside a pine-framed papyrus beneath a brass lantern.  An embroidered curtain covering the wagon's entry wavers from an errant breeze.
